                    <div class="eight wide center aligned column">
                        <div class="servir_otherPages_text_subTitle">
                            This tool allows development practitioners, scientists/researchers, and government decision-makers to visualize and download historical rainfall data, vegetation condition data, and 180-day forecasts of rainfall and temperature to improve understanding of, and make improved decisions for, issues related to agriculture and water availability.
                        </div>
